        "catTechnical": "Technical Support",
        "faq1Q": "How do I book a movie ticket?",
        "faq1A": "Simply go to our Home page, select a movie, choose your preferred cinema and showtime, then select your seats and proceed to payment. You can also book directly from the Movie detail page.",
        "faq2Q": "Can I modify or cancel my booking?",
        "faq2A": "Yes, you can modify or cancel your booking up to 2 hours before the showtime. Go to your Account → Booking History, find the booking and select Modify or Cancel. Please note that some fees may apply depending on the fare type.",
        "faq3Q": "What payment methods are accepted?",
        "faq3A": "We accept major credit/debit cards (Visa, MasterCard), bank transfers, digital wallets (Google Pay, Apple Pay), and reward points. All payments are processed securely through our encrypted payment gateway.",
        "faq4Q": "How do I create an account?",
        "faq4A": "Click on 'Sign In' in the top navigation bar, then select 'Register'. Fill in your details including name, email, and phone number. You can also sign up quickly using your Google account.",
        "faq5Q": "How can I reset my password?",
        "faq5A": "On the login page, click 'Forgot Password'. Enter your registered email address and we will send you a password reset link. The link expires in 24 hours for security reasons.",
        "faq6Q": "How do refunds work?",
        "faq6A": "Refunds are processed to your original payment method within 5-7 business days. Cancellation fees may apply. For bookings made with reward points, points will be returned to your account.",
        "faq7Q": "Why is the website not loading properly?",
        "faq7A": "Try clearing your browser cache and cookies, or try using a different browser. Ensure your internet connection is stable. If the problem persists, contact our support team.",
        "faq8Q": "How do I enable notifications?",
        "faq8A": "Go to your Account Settings and enable push notifications. You can choose to receive alerts for upcoming bookings, special offers, and new movie releases. Make sure your browser allows notifications for this site."
    },
